  "text": "Exercise after nerve injury has been reported to suppress spinal neuroimmune signaling induced by nerve injury. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] Therefore, we investigated whether prior running normalized the expression of 2 neuroimmune signaling pathways in the dorsal spinal cord at 3 and 14 days after CCI.",
